
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Join the list · The Artyst</title>
<meta name="description" content="Sign up to The Artyst's email list — events, exhibitions, news from the Invysible College and Cambridge tours.">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1a1a;
    --ink-soft: #4a4a4a;
    --ink-faint: #6a6a6a;
    --paper: #fafaf8;
    --line: #e5e3dc;
    --accent: #1d5c5c;
    --accent-soft: #e8f2f1;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { font-size: 16px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Charter", "Georgia", "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
  }
  main {
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  p.intro {
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }
  label {
    display: block;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  label .optional {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
  }
  input[type="email"], input[type="text"] {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.875rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }
  input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-soft);
  }
  /* Honeypot — hidden from users, present for bots */
  .hp {
    position: absolute;
    left: -9999px;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  button {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  button:hover {
    background: #164848;
  }
  .small-print {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .small-print a {
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .small-print a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .signoff {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    h1 { font-size: 1.625rem; }
    p.intro { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <div class="eyebrow">The Artyst</div>
  <h1>Join the list.</h1>

  <p class="intro">Around one email a fortnight — events at the venue, exhibitions, news from the Invysible College and our Cambridge walking tours. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>

  <form method="POST" action="/api/subscribe/signup" autocomplete="on">
    <label for="email">Email</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="name@example.com" required autocomplete="email">

    <label for="first_name">First name <span class="optional">— optional</span></label>
    <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" placeholder="Jane" maxlength="50" autocomplete="given-name">

    <!-- Honeypot field — humans don't fill this in, bots do. Hidden via CSS. -->
    <div class="hp" aria-hidden="true">
      <label for="website">Website</label>
      <input type="text" id="website" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Join the list</button>
  </form>

  <p class="small-print">
    By submitting, you agree to receive emails from The Artyst at the address above. We'll send you a confirmation email — your subscription only goes live once you click the link inside it. We won't share your details with anyone. <a href="/privacy">Privacy policy</a>.
  </p>

  <p class="signoff">The Artyst · 54–56 Chesterton Road · Cambridge CB4 1EN</p>
</main>
</body>
</html>
